•	Client UI and administrator UI
•	A valid SSL certificate
•	The back-end and front-end applications communicating through APIs for security
•	Clients must be able to make, reschedule or cancel an online appointment
•	The business should be able to confirm or reject or reschedule appointments
•	Client should be able to choose a payment method
•	Capturing and monitoring of analytics
•	Ability to customize application by using an admin client/application
